    <h1 class="mb-4">Best Way to Appear on Google Gemini 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on testing across 1,400+ UK business websites</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Google Gemini is integrated into Google Search, Android, Gmail and Google Workspace. It draws from the Google Knowledge Graph, your Google Business Profile, Google Reviews and the search index. If Google understands your business, Gemini likely will too. But understanding and recommending are not the same thing.</p>

    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">These are the 10 most effective methods to move from "Google knows you exist" to "Gemini recommends you." Each method is ranked by impact and effort, based on our testing across 1,400+ UK business websites.</p>

