      <p class="text-[15px] text-teal font-medium leading-relaxed m-0"><strong>Key insight:</strong> Gemini is the AI platform most influenced by your Google presence. If your Google Business Profile is incomplete or your reviews are thin, Gemini has less to recommend. Start there.</p>
