      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-6">Frequently asked questions</h2>

      <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Is Gemini the same as Google AI Overviews?</h3>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">No. Gemini is Google's conversational AI, available at gemini.google.com and through the Gemini app. AI Overviews are the AI-generated summaries that appear at the top of Google Search results. They use similar technology but pull from different contexts. Optimising for one helps with the other, but they are distinct products.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Does my Google ranking affect Gemini?</h3>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">Yes, more than any other AI platform. Gemini draws heavily from Google Search results, Knowledge Graph and Google Business Profile. If you rank well on Google, you are already in Gemini's data pool. The methods above help you move from being in the data pool to being actively recommended.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Can I optimise for Gemini separately from Google Search?</h3>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">Most Gemini optimisation is good Google optimisation. The main additions are ensuring your GBP is complete, your entity data is consistent, and your content is structured for extraction. If you are already doing solid SEO, Gemini optimisation is mostly about tightening gaps in your Google ecosystem presence.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Does Gemini use Google Reviews?</h3>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">Yes. Gemini references review sentiment and volume when recommending businesses, particularly for local queries. It does not just look at your star rating. It reads what customers say and factors that into its recommendations.</p>

      <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">How quickly can I appear on Gemini?</h3>
      <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">If you already rank well on Google and have a complete GBP, improvements can show within days. Building authority from scratch takes 3 to 6 months. The fastest wins come from completing your Google Business Profile and fixing entity inconsistencies, as these feed directly into Gemini's data sources.</p>
